name: O'Charley's Famous Chicken Tender Eating Simulator
name_original: O'Charley's Famous Chicken Tender Eating Simulator
description:
Introducing O'Charley's Famous Chicken Tender Eating Simulator! This is a very high-quality game that I didn't just make in an hour! 

Features

- Eat O'Charley's Famous Chicken Tenders

- Eat more O'Charley's Famous Chicken Tenders

- Eat even more O'Charley's Famous Chicken Tenders!

This game has nothing to do with the O'Charley's brand and is simply a crappy game based on an inside joke.
